title: Giants draft recap + O/U lookahead, Browns post-draft trade rumors (Football 05/01)
description:
Nick Kostos joins Will Brinson to break down the rumors about the Browns being unable to trade down, Jason Witten retiring (?) and what it means for the Cowboys, whether the Eagles were trolling the Cowboys, which team is his lead pipe LOCK for over/unders this coming season, which teams interest the two of them in terms of over/under bets, whether the Giants had a good draft, how he looks at their roster, what he thinks of the Saquon Barkley pick and if the Giants will be any good in 2018.
